{
  "stem": "1511.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I want to survive because I want to see my family back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want to live through and see my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was keeping me going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made-- we couldn't come together and pray.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was places where we hide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we found somebody who can daven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were doing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we had one place where all the refugees used to come together, and one find out from the other, little by little.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in Russia, it wasn't allowed to do all these things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't have a Jewish paper or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they put all these people in jail, and they never came out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] did a lot for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They baked matzos for Pesach, everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a big underground from the [NON-ENGLISH] what, they help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They want us to be Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- we knew-- we knew that they are there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to help for there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were a great help to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were a lot, a lot of people in them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what happened after that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, you worked in the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were dealing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day she says like that, she says, you know what, Sally-- my name was Salka-- how about if I get a bunch of clothes, and if you want to go to Chkalov-- it's another two, three months just to go.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's the end of the Russian border, close to the White Bear, someplace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very, very cold there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's a long journey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I supposed to have a ticket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it's not so easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
